          "diff_summary": "--- before\n+++ after\n@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@\n <!-- wp:html --><!-- AI_SLOT:INTRO -->\n-<p><strong>Newcastle Hub</strong> builds fast, conversion-focused websites and measurable marketing for local businesses in Newcastle.</p>\n+<p>Newcastle Hub helps local Newcastle businesses build fast, conversion-focused websites and measurable marketing strategies that turn visitors into customers. Whether you're a small business owner looking to establish an online presence or an established company wanting to improve your digital performance, this page covers everything you need to know about getting a professional website built quickly without sacrificing quality. By combining rapid development timelines with proven marketing tactics and transparent results tracking, Newcastle Hub ensures your investment directly impacts your bottom line.</p>\n <!-- /AI_SLOT:INTRO -->\n <!-- AI_SLOT:FAQ -->\n <style>.ai-faq-accordion details{margin:0 0 18px;border:1px solid var(--nc-border-color);border-radius:12px;background:#fff;overflow:hidden}.ai-faq-accordion summary{cursor:pointer;list-style:none;padding:16px 18px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.6}.ai-faq-accordion summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}.ai-faq-accordion details[open] summary{border-bottom:1px solid var(--nc-section-bg)}.ai-faq-accordion p{margin:0;padding:16px 18px 18px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--nc-text-secondary)}</style>",
